question: Tī 'Initial volatility', 'Long-term volatility', kap 'Mean reversion speed' ê ōe, ē-tàng tùi chit-ê model teh sî-kan lāi-té ê volatility piàn-hòa lâi teh sím-mih?
answer: Chit-ê model hián-sī mean-reverting volatility. 'Long-term volatility' siat tī 0.3, chit-ê chòe-ūi óa-tè. 'Initial volatility' ē-tàng khai-sí khah-koân (0.4), khah-kē (0.2), ia̍h-sī tī long-term ê téng-téng (0.3). Bô-lūn sī tó-ūi khai-sí, volatility lóng ē-tàng hiòng 0.3 chìn-hêng, chit-ê koè-têng sī iû 'Mean reversion speed' 2.0 lâi koán-lí. Chia̍t-sok piáu-sī koân-volatility ia̍h-sī kē-volatility ê sî-kî bē-sī éng-kiú.

question: Chhâ 'Market Dynamics' chit-ê lūi-pia̍t ē-té, só͘-ūi chhut-hiān chòe chē-ê khó-lêng-sèng ê chhú-ta̍t-ta̍t (value), i-ê só͘-ū chhú-ta̍t-ta̍t lóng bô-huí ê chhiūⁿ-tāi-tiâu ê chhú-ta̍t-ta̍t (non-negative).

Nā-kā 'Risk aversion' tō-sī kóng pīⁿ gûi-hiám sū-iōng ê hōan-hoān, nā 'Permanent impact' kap 'Temporary impact' ê siōng-sū lóng kā-tī seng-ka 10 pōe, 'Temporary impact coefficient' kap 'Risk aversion' ê sin pí-lē sī siáⁿ-mih?

Nā-sū 'Mean reversion speed' 若減少 50%, kāng-chiah 'Volatility of variance' ê giá trị lóng-chóng kāng-chiap kiā-chiū 0.1, chia̍h-sio̍k 'Mean reversion speed' kap siōng-tōa 'Volatility of variance' ê pōaⁿ-sò͘ sī sím-mi̍h?

Chia̍h-tiàu-á piáu-khai 'Correlation' ê tsu-liāu sī -0.7. Tī tsit-ê kim-iông bôo-hîng lāi-té, tsit-ê tsiânn-tsē hū-siōng tsu-liāu it-puann teh tāi-piáu tio̍h tsi̍t-ê tsá-khì kè-siōng kah i-ê kuânn-tōng-sèng tsi-kan ê kuan-hē?
answer: Correlation sī -0.7 piáu-sī tsit-ê tsá-khì kah kuânn-tōng-sèng chi-kan ū tsiânn-tsē kòe-ē kuan-hē, it-ti̍t kiò-tsò leveraged effect. I piáu-sī, nā tsá-khì kè-siōng kàng-kē, i-ê kuânn-tōng-sèng khuah-tāi; tsi̍t-kang nā tsá-khì kè-siōng tsiánn-tsē, i-ê kuânn-tōng-sèng lūi-tông kàng-kē. Tsit-ê tsiánn-tsē tiōng-iàu, teh si̍t-tsai tsá-khì kè-siōng bôo-hîng kah guā-tsè ting-kè.

question: Tī chia̍h-ê piáu-keh lāi-té, ū kúi-ê chham-sò͘ sī iōng chē-ê khó-lêng ê sò͘-tiāu lâi tēng-gī, bô-sī kan-na chi̍t-ê kò͘-tēng ê sò͘-tiāu?
Sui-chi̍t ê tsit-ê tsia̍t-sòo sī tsi̍t-ê kuān-tsit tsi-tsa̍t, in-uī i-ê kè-siàu tsí-ū tsit-ê sī hū-siōng?
